Package: cryptoAPIs
Type: Package
Title: Cryptocurrency Exchange API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tidy wrappers for cryptocurrency exchange REST APIs
    including Upbit, Bithumb, GOPAX, Coinone, Korbit, Binance, Coinbase, and OKX.
    Functions cover trading pair lookup, recent OHLCV data, historical range
    data, and market risk alarm retrieval.
